{"tid":1653313,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"光头刘蛇：政治就是心狠手辣","createTime":"2019-10-14T04:28:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-14T12:01:23.000Z","uid":184679,"like":18,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":66,"replies":[{"pid":"d61abb7f2fe0c6a8012d51749958a473dde4fc77","tid":1653313,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T04:28:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.orangenews.hk/pic/0/10/23/09/10230966_376900.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.orangenews.hk%2Fpic%2F0%2F10%2F23%2F09%2F10230966_376900.jpg&h=6fe5697b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「光頭警長」劉澤基因在葵涌遭示威者包圍期間，舉起雷明登霰彈槍嚇退人群，近日成為內地網紅，不時發文表達意見。他今早在個人微博表示，「禁蒙面法絕對有用，但未夠有用。」他認為，香港需要宵禁，令暴徒走出來，便觸犯法例，他又倡將「連登網站」及「民陣」列作恐怖組織，將他們的資金凍結直接「炒家」。<br />\n<br />\n劉澤基在微博又說，「我們需要將記者由政府發牌登記，他們根本就是暴徒的幫凶！」，他直言政治就是心狠手辣，不夠狠怎能達到目的。「治亂世用重典，此乃打擊罪犯不二法門！」<br />\n<br />\n不少網民對其言論表示議論紛紛，有人認同他的建議，指「政府應考慮」，又指他是一個「好的政治家」、「愛國愛港典範」；但亦有人批評他「當自己係大總統？」、「看來劉Sir對政治很有研究」。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">http://www.orangenews.hk/news/system/2019/10/14/010128775.shtml</code></pre>"},{"pid":"18fc8d0e88f560ca44561d3e8f87232e8439a2ff","tid":1653313,"uid":323443,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T04:31:23.000Z","msg":"忘了自己是誰"},{"pid":"64ab600b27492606ea7031370dfa2501e0c71b3b","tid":1653313,"uid":271434,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T04:33:16.000Z","msg":"警要新仔幫上頭及大陸武警嘅罪行頂罪<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1651133\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1651133</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"fc73551d90825cd85c1532cee0500fc4815889ef","tid":1653313,"uid":14918,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T04:34:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20090417/large/17ec7p1new.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fap